Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:33.92,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be \Nlike this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:40.22,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from \Nthis saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:45.98,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:49.73,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:52.74,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:59.83,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the \Nconfusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:05.25,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:10.96,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times \Nand then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:14.17,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.38,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:22.93,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, \NI'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.02,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:29.44,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:35.03,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know \Nanything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:41.41,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining \Nlight in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.99,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Nine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.99,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku's Crime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.99,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi's\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Detective Stories)\N "Sneering Demon" and "Red Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.46,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}I recommend turning comments off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.75,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}Why doesn't the mainstream press report this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.67,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}They went and shot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.79,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}Ouch! Better not fuck with the guys upstairs, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.79,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}This is gonna get taken down ASAP...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.08,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,Leaked Company Profit Report\NPoster: Full Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.42,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious of a Lover?\NPoster: Full Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.30,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are a lot \Nof uploads like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.01,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This one and this one and this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.84,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The posters are Full Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.22,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They say the whole \Nworld is "one circle".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.27,Main Dialog,Koyamada,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:12.56,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, these crackers have \Nstarted targeting JJ Systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.07,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They're on a roll, leaking everything \Nfrom in-house accounting documents
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:19.41,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,to info on Chairman Kaishou \NRinroku's private affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}So cute~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}{\i1}She’s{\i0} Kaishou's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}My waifu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}Hot damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}The daughter of the upper crust, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}The horse is so cool!!!www
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.62,Caption Top,Comments,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}Cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:26.70,Main Dialog,Koyamada,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of stuff can be taken down \Nquickly with automated monitoring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.42,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But there are those who \Ncan get around that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.67,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Like they did with a certain song...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.71,Name White,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Koyama Izumi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.71,Name Sub White,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Public Prosecutor\N Joint Coordinating Dept.\N Public Prosecutor's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.71,Name White,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Oyamada Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.71,Name Sub White,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Underground Software Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.17,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think nobody noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.22,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,In the Joint Coordinating Department...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.72,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Even you must realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.85,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,She turns the words of a \Ncertain person into reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Or at the very least, she has the \Nability to make it seem that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.41,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Bettenou escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.99,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:11.46,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you intend to \Nacquire Bettenou yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.92,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The police and Kaishou are searching \Nfor her whereabouts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.92,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find her before they do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.22,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,And what do we do when we find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.51,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Kazamori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.51,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Artificial Intelligence (R.A.I.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.68,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.89,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,If what you say is true, \NBettenou isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.68,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, she hasn't \Ncommitted any crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.94,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Yuuki Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.94,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.23,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she's committed crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:33.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:38.28,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou, it's not a good idea \Nto get too close to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.65,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Inga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.65,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.15,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou-sama, you've got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.71,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.83,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,We already put out the \Nbreaking announcement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.04,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,and now Professor Kaishou doesn't show?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.63,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyama Minami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.63,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Television Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.26,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's Full Circle again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.55,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}AD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.55,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Motoyama's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.43,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Can I watch anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:11.31,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Kaishou Rinroku is \Ngoing to be on TV right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.85,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,A person that everyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.44,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,is going to make a last second \Nappearance live on our show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:36.96,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}The Roundtable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.48,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The Chairman of JJ \NSystems, Kaishou Rinroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.44,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,This is the man who is working \Nhard to quickly reconstruct
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.86,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,the telephone and internet systems \Nthat were targeted during the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.66,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,while at the same time solving \Na great number of criminal cases
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.95,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,as an adviser to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:34.58,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaishou has requested the \Nopportunity to speak about today's theme,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.63,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,legislation to nationalize \Nthe energy industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.96,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,And we're in commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.42,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few moments ago, an odd post \Nclaiming to be from Full Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.30,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,has appeared on various bulletin \Nboards and major social networks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.93,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.85,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,It seems our lives are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:01.78,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is Kaishou Rinroku going \Nto appear on that TV program?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.28,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,"Actually, the other participants
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.57,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,are a politician who's been \Ncritical of JJ Systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:09.28,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,the owner of a rival company, and a \Ncritic who released a tell-all book..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.99,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,"In other words, all enemies \Nof Kaishou Rinroku."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:17.17,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could Chairman Kaishou's sudden \Nrequest to be on the show be because of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.58,Main Dialog,Politician,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.75,Main Dialog,Politician,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Chairman \NKaishou of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.88,Main Dialog,Politician,0000,0000,0000,,would murder us on a public TV program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.72,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Full Circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.39,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't they recently expose you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.85,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Fuwa Jujirou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.85,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Solar Power Advocate, Entrepreneur
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:34.22,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,for putting out government propaganda \Nnews reports during the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.19,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that doesn't have a \Ndirect connection to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.52,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,So what about Mr. Kaishou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.27,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really going to show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.65,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:45.65,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming he actually exists \Nin the first place... {missed sign?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.74,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.08,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.79,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my lateness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.71,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't taken the train for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.54,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You took the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.54,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.76,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.30,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.30,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Chairman of JJ Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.30,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,This should be a heated discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:14.18,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, the Master's program \Nis about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.97,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Family Maid (Head Maid)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.97,Name Sub,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.43,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.98,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Again with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.60,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're secretly \Ngoing to watch it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.35,Name,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.35,Name Sub,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter of Kaishou Rinroku, Lives at Home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.23,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, a cockroach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:32.24,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,He looks good on camera, \NI have to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.08,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.58,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.21,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.38,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.63,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,From home, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.38,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.05,Main Dialog,Critic,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's consulting someone \Nabout wiping us all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.88,Main Dialog,Politician,0000,0000,0000,,Like all of a sudden, boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.31,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.57,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'm not good with machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.49,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the difference \Nbetween a crack and a hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.87,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is Full Circle \Ntargeting Chairman Kaishou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.91,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They're leaking too much \Npersonal information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're by yourself today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.33,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a public holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.92,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, I had to drive myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.92,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.88,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the site...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:31.55,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god! And what about the Chairman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.89,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What about Chairman Kaishou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.60,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,The TV station's server is down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.14,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,The nearby fixed cameras...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.87,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.84,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Quickly! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.44,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,He may call the house, so stay put!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.82,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Check the email, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.40,Main Dialog,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:31.99,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Please just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.15,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,You stay home, Rie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.83,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.20,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But... That was a live show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.16,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,I appeared via private \Nwebcam from the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.87,Main Dialog,Kaishou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to see \Nwhat's happening over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.63,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But... They said it was \Na live appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.09,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.64,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll be satisfied \Nwith, "He's not here"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.47,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Prosecutor! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.98,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.48,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Hayami Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.48,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Director of the Security Bureau \NMetropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.57,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.70,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Hospital, hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.01,Name,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.14,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Eight people have been \Nlisted as missing or dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.97,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,among them the participants \Nin a live TV program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.02,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Word from the hospital is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:49.02,Main Dialog,Male Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,We're told that there was antipathy \Nbetween Mr. Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.77,Main Dialog,Male Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,and the president of Solar Field, Fuwa \NJujirou, who's been badly injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.40,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Kaishou Rinroku will eliminate \Nthose who stand in his way."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.53,Main Dialog,Male Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Strangely enough, Full Circle's \Nprediction has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.82,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.12,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,And that was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.53,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the hospital here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Inga... Where the \Nhell did you wander off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.75,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Keep out! Everyone, keep out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.75,Caption Top,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}Explosion during a popular debate television program...\NLive from the hospital where the injured are being treated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.80,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Public Security \NForce doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:20.14,Caption Top,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}8 people dead or missing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.51,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're in charge of private \Nsecurity for Chairman Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.93,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,We dropped him off at a \NTV station yesterday too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.14,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,but to think this could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.89,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's allowed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.39,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a fever. Maybe a cold...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.77,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Or it could be the flu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't get some medicine, \NI think I'm gonna keel over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.56,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,The Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.78,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably the one who \Ntargeted Professor Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.78,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Mizuno Sakon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.78,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Public Security Force Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.53,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mizuno, the commander of \Nthe Public Security Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.20,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mihara, one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.58,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Mihara Yasutarou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.58,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Public Security Force,\NCommanded by Mizuno
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.04,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're around, you're not \Ngetting anywhere near Professor Kaishou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.66,Main Dialog,Female Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yajima! You were here to pay a \Nvisit to Chairman Kaishou, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.08,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Yajima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.08,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Critic
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.08,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a friend \Nof his from way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.13,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and if this hadn't happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.30,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,he would be working now as \Nalways, around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.59,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this will serve as \Na chance for him to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.59,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Was the perpetrator \Nafter Mr. Kaishou? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.01,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.27,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not certain that \Nthis was terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.31,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the station is very old
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.27,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,and I heard it's possible \Nthat this was just a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.28,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,Please let this person through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.74,Main Dialog,Yajima,0000,0000,0000,,He's an acquaintance of Ms. Kaishou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.99,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Defeated Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.99,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Unusually enough, you were successful \Nwith Mr. Yajima's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.54,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let it go to your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.37,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,414\NKaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.96,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is just as \NFull Circle predicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.01,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,We were almost killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.92,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,And the criminal is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:45.10,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If Chairman Kaishou had taken one wrong \Nstep, he would have lost his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.27,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Right! He just happened \Nto leave the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.73,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,the moment before the \Nexplosion occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.56,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.81,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Who would ever believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:57.48,Main Dialog,Fuwa,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Anyway, I'm not \Ntaking this lying down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:16.96,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father's condition would \Nget worse if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.71,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you call me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.92,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,About the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.81,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it seem like the culprit \Nis Kaishou Rinroku himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.22,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.98,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:38.77,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, I can't say \Nthat he's a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:41.40,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But he wouldn't do something as stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.24,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,as gathering together people who \Ndisagree with him and then killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, he would commit \Nthe perfect crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.83,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,which no one would ever suspect him of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.99,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is my fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.13,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.15,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,What did you talk to her about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What do the police think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.36,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What was the cause of the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.45,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,The military is investigating, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.78,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't seem to have \Nbeen a normal explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.91,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought, me, having \Nto prove Kaishou's innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.63,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Is Inga still lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.38,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.89,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a member of the \NDiet can get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.60,Main Dialog,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,A Diet summons at a time like \Nthis shows no common sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.60,Caption Top,Mihara,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Note: The Japanese Diet has a constitutional power to compel any citizen to come testify before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:57.85,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.36,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.70,Name White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kuramitsu Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.70,Name Sub White,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,New Diet Member
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.11,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.16,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of the Diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.66,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Just a newly-elected errand girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.70,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,I told them it was impossible today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.33,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,but they ordered me to get \NChairman Kaishou's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.83,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You mean as a witness to \Nyesterday's explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.80,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.22,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,The internal information that Full \NCircle released the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.05,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,talked about a system that could be \Ndiverted to part of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.89,Main Dialog,Shinjirou,0000,0000,0000,,It was information from JJ Systems?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.89,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,We just want him to explain \Nfor some foreign countries
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.06,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,that the system is designed \Nfor peaceful purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:41.90,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Microwave transmissions \Nor something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.36,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,The live TV broadcast date \Nhas already been set, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being he'll need his rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Hard luck for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.95,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,The cause was microwaves?\NLive aerial footage from the explosion site
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.00,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.83,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,No! {\i1}Train{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying Kaishou \Ncame here by train?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:07.17,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,No! I said he came here by {\i1}train{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What did he seem like at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:17.77,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,There was that thing with Full Circle, \Nso we were worried, but he was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:22.56,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, doing it like that, \Nhe would've gotten blown up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.32,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be a pansy about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:27.15,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you melt the range?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.82,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.87,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.37,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,The microwave, it's the microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.45,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's talking about what \Nhappened yesterday on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.21,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,People are wondering whether the \Ncause might be military microwaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.21,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same principle as \Nputting metal in a microwave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.96,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,and it crackles with electricity, \Nsuddenly producing high heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.09,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,We're being told that the \Ncause of the accident
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.76,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,was the dilapidated station building,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:55.14,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm gonna prove that wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.35,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,It's all scientific-like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:04.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure some people are \Nsaying that JJ Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.86,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,used microwaves to cause the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.40,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way someone would have \Nthat fired at a building they were in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.70,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm proving him innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.16,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.25,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.04,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.29,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father... was at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:33.38,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,My father wasn't at the TV \Nstation. He was at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.93,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,But later, I got a phone \Ncall from the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.93,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,saying my father had been \Ninjured at the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.89,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,The producer says my father \Nwas at the studio, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.52,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a doppelganger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.65,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Unless someone disguised \Nhimself as my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.16,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.28,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.41,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning your fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.96,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.47,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think my father is the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it all to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.48,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Shinjurou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.74,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.61,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.41,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Inga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out where Bettenou is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Many people have testified \Nthat Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,was at the TV station at \Nthe time of that explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yet his own flesh and blood insists \Nhe was at home at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The same kind of thing \Nhappened once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.01,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.18,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bettenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The believers in the Bettenou \NSociety saw what wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.27,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,They even saw hallucinations \Nthrough the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what the Kaishou that \Nappeared at the TV station was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.02,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,We dropped him off at a TV \Nstation yesterday too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.98,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,I said he came here by {\i1}train{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It was a hallucination, \Nso the details conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The day Bettenou disappeared \Nfrom the Novelist's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.37,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Bettenou was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.29,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:30.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaishou says "Bettenou isn't \Nhere", then Bettenou can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:34.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Inga, you too... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.97,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mad about, Shinjurou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:43.18,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Mad?! You can use Bettenou to \Nturn any lie into the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:46.35,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think Kaishou was the kind of \Nguy who'd rely on something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to prove that \Nbastard's innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:53.11,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... You can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.95,Main Dialog,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Inga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.74,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, \NI'm gonna get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.25,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna corner him \Nwhere he can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Diet Member Kuramitsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:15.50,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Yuuki Shinjurou,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:18.26,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Kuramitsu Mine\N"I'm heading to the future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm calling about the summoning \Nfor the live broadcast testimony...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:21.97,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Amid all this, it's been decided \Nthat Mr. Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.14,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,will be summoned as a witness before \Nthe National Diet's budget committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.56,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do \Nwith the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.81,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Diet Member Kuramitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:38.90,Caption Top,Captions,0000,0000,0000,,Testimony Live from his hospital bed\NKaishou Rinroku Summoned to Testify
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.36,Main Dialog,Other Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The Chairman has expressed a desire \Nto testify from the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.19,Main Dialog,Other Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,but will he maintain his innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:39.40,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm just a low-ranking \Nmember, so I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.24,Main Dialog,Female Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible to murder \Nwith a microwave satellite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:46.16,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, the purpose is to have him \Nanswer the suspicions of foreign nations,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.66,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,and he is not suspected \Nof murder at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.62,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.04,Main Dialog,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make a severely \Ninjured man testify?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.72,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.80,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.80,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to separate the footage \Nand voice that we record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.93,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to replace the voice \Nwith a computer generated one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.81,Main Dialog,AD,0000,0000,0000,,so the real voice of the person \Ntestifying won't be broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.07,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Chairman Kaishou's voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.03,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,but it's actually from a \Nvocal synthesizing program.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.53,Main Dialog,Motoyama,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.32,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that classified \Ninformation will be brought up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.79,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,so just in case, I want \Nto have a time lag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:38.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If Bettenou's power is \Ncontrolling people via voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,then switching that with an \Nartificial voice should stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.76,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't strike me as the type \Nto talk to a cute stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.60,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a present from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:52.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I use it in place of a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.48,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.82,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,Your advice was right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.99,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,His daughter persuaded \Nhim when I told her
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.11,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,that her father's innocence \Nshould be broadcast on live TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.45,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,But about those conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.62,Main Dialog,Kuramitsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:15.12,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it a good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:35.94,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the pale morning \Nmist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:43.94,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna follow this \Ntwisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:51.95,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the "truth", \N"a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:22:00.38,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:04.26,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:08.26,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:11.26,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:16.69,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:36.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:40.25,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:43.13,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:48.30,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:54.35,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The preview this time too is inspired \Nby "Red Trap" from Ango Torimonochou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:57.56,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of this pattern! It's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:58.89,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The original idea was a segment of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:01.19,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,not being able to read the original \Nstory and riffing on the gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:04.02,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,and riffing on the gap \Nbetween it and modern stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:06.24,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,But the scriptwriter has \Ntotally forgotten that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.95,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,and only just remembered \Nnow, but it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.41,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I laid it out straight! You \Ngot a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.41,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on UN-GO: "Kaishou \NRinroku's Funeral".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.41,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaishou Rinroku's Funeral"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.41,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by "Sneering Demon" and "Red Trap" from Ango Sakaguchi's\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Detective Stories)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.21,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right! He's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:19.42,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?!
